OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShop sales slow as people  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frein in spending           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sales in shops have slowed as household
OL,6, budgets come under pressure from the   
OL,7, rising cost of living, the British     
OL,8, Retail Consortium (BRC) has said.      
OL,10,FIts figures show sales growth for March
OL,11,Frose by 3.1%, the smallest increase so 
OL,12,Ffar this year and down from a 6.7% rise
OL,13,Fin February.                           
OL,15,FIt comes as millions are having to deal
OL,16,Fwith higher energy bills and taxes.    
OL,18,FThe BRC said pressure on people's      
OL,19,Ffinances and the war in Ukraine had    
OL,20,F"shaken consumer confidence".          
